	<h1 class="title">阿迪达斯发狠出了 50 种颜色的新板鞋</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/49585/small/49585.jpg?1422286480" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马安琪</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-27 13:35:19 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7863/medium/7863.png?1436694294" alt="" />			
	</div>
